gmoji\" />"},{"pid":"54ba37fd55c1c94a08dc553fc76ac4683a45d69f","tid":2323150,"uid":32454,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:25:27.000Z","msg":"米醫師巴打型好多= ="},{"pid":"a3ef24ece77e4e4de9ab10f93da25a81a73d8970","tid":2323150,"uid":346084,"like":12,"dislike":0,"score":12,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:29:54.000Z","msg":"咁就喺呢度順便講下我地遇過嘅挫折啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n由於我地兩個一個住北區 一個住九龍西 真好難成日見面去傾 之後我地膽粗粗租左個臨時辦公室開始左我地嘅夢<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n設計 布料 同廠家磋商 到成品 擺貨地方 全部都要我地去面對<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/ass.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去到呢度諗住已經踏入大直路 只能說少年 太年輕鳥<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/369.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n我地同第一個廠商整左數十件成品出來 結果不如理想 要報銷 真係深受打擊<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n但我地依然無放棄到 繼續去聯絡第二個廠家 結果又遇到困難 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/@.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n因為對方要求我地一個款式最少要幾百件 佢地先會起貨<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/donno.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n對於兩個剛剛撞板嘅傻仔 再要我地投放更多資金 真係好大風險<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n但我地掙扎左好耐 覺得值得博多一次 就決定去馬 結果就真係出左一批我地滿意嘅成品 <img src=\"/assets/faces/big/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f59b1c6627d217b937c11dad7e706dc2b4a170af","tid":2323150,"uid":99929,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:30:45.000Z","msg":"人血饅頭好好食"},{"pid":"76cc40d3b7b720c6e0bf9ec60a2796f98c893234","tid":2323150,"uid":375135,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"969a2e69feea68efb90ea832289143697f411420","tid":2323150,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-12-13T03:00:47.000Z","msg":"採得百花成蜜後 為誰辛苦為誰甜<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FGSLT